Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Haig questioned by Senate committee
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b043w5ss
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 18 Jan 1981
General Haig faces five-day appearance before Senate committee. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014.